{"title_page": "European route E01 in Ireland", "text_new": "{{Unreferenced|date=May 2019|bot=noref (GreenC bot)}}\nThe [[European route E01]] in the [[Republic of Ireland]] is a serie of roads, part of the [[International E-road network]] running in a north south axis on the Irish east coast. It runs through five [[Counties of Ireland|counties]] starting on the [[United Kingdom|British]] border with the province of [[Northern Ireland]] at [[Dundalk]], coming from [[Belfast]] and [[Larne]]. It passes the capital [[Dublin]] until it stops at [[Rosslare Harbour]] in Southern [[Republic of Ireland|Ireland]]. From there the E01 crosses the [[Celtic Sea]] and the [[Bay of Biscay]] on a non-existent [[ferry]] towards [[Spain]] and [[Portugal]].\n\n== Route ==\nThe [[European route E01|E01]] comes from [[Northern Ireland]] when it crosses the border at [[Dundalk]] where the [[United Kingdom|British]] [[A1 road (Northern Ireland)|A1 road]] changes to the [[Republic of Ireland|Irish]] N1 road until northern [[Dundalk]]. It then follows the [[M1 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M1 motorway]] to [[Drogheda]] and eventually the [[capital city|capital]] [[Dublin]]. After using the [[M50 motorway (Ireland)|M50]] ring road around [[Dublin]], the E01 uses the [[N11 road (Ireland)|N11 road]] and [[M11 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M11 motorway]] passing [[Bray, County Wicklow|Bray]], [[Wicklow]], [[Gorey]] and [[Enniscorthy]] to [[Wexford]]. The last part is the [[N25 road (Ireland)|N25 road]] towards [[Rosslare Harbour]]. The E01 covers a total distance of 266&nbsp;km (165&nbsp;mi) in the [[Republic of Ireland]].\n\n== Detailed route ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+<big>E01 Dundalk - Rosslare</big>\n!County\n!National\nroad\n\nnumber\n!Section\n!Junction\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|United Kingdom}}{{Flagicon|Northern Ireland}}\n|[[File:UK road A1.svg|frameless|38x38px]] [[A1 road (Northern Ireland)|A1 road]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Flag|UK}} from [[Larne]] to border with Republic of Ireland via [[Belfast]], [[Lisburn]] and [[Newry]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Flagicon|EU}}{{Flagicon|Ireland}}{{Flagicon|Leinster}}[[County Louth|Louth]]\n|[[File:IRL N1.svg|frameless|50x50px]][[N1 road (Ireland)|N1 road]]\n|[[Northern Ireland]]-[[Dundalk]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 20 [[R132 road (Ireland)|R132]] Carrickcarnan, {{Flag|UK}} ([[Jonesborough, County Armagh|Jonesborough]])\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 19 R174 [[Ravensdale, County Louth|Ravensdale]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 18 [[N52 road (Ireland)|N52]] [[Dundalk]] (North), [[Carlingford, County Louth|Carlingford]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[File:M1_motorway_IE.png|frameless|56x56px]][[M1 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M1 motorway]]\n|[[Dundalk]]-[[Drogheda]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 17 [[N53 road (Ireland)|N53]] [[Dundalk]] (Center), [[Castleblayney]], [[Monaghan]]\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 16 [[N52 road (Ireland)|N52]] [[Dundalk]] (South), [[Ardee]], [[Mullingar]]\n\n[[File:Zeichen 376 - Autobahngasthaus (600x600), StVO 1992.svg|frameless|28x28px]] [[File:Zeichen_361-51.svg|frameless|28x28px]] [[Castlebellingham]] service station\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 15 [[R166 road (Ireland)|R166]] [[Castlebellingham]], [[Tallanstown]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 14 [[N33 road (Ireland)|N33]], [[N2 road (Ireland)|N2]] [[Ardee]], [[Monaghan]], {{Flag|UK}} ([[Derry]])\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 13 R170 [[Dunleer]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 12 R169 [[Dunleer]], [[Collon]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 11 [[R132 road (Ireland)|R132]] [[Monasterboice]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 10 [[N51 road (Ireland)|N51]] [[Drogheda]] (North), [[Navan]], [[Slane]], [[Our Lady of Lourdes Hospital, Drogheda|Hospital]]\n|-\n|[[County Meath|Meath]]\n|[[Drogheda]]-[[Balbriggan]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 9 [[Drogheda]], [[Donore, County Meath|Donore]], [[Duleek]]\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 8 [[Drogheda]], [[Duleek]]\n\n[[File:Ireland_Road_Toll_Symbol.png|frameless|25x25px]] near [[Julianstown]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 7 [[Julianstown]], [[Laytown]], [[Stamullen]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[County Dublin|Dublin]]\n|[[Balbriggan]]-[[Dublin]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 6 [[R122 road (Ireland)|R122]] [[Balbriggan]], [[Skerries, Dublin|Skerries]], [[Naul, Dublin|Naul]]\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 5 [[R132 road (Ireland)|R132]] [[Balbriggan]], [[Lusk, Dublin|Lusk]], [[Rush, Dublin|Rush]]\n\n[[File:Zeichen 376 - Autobahngasthaus (600x600), StVO 1992.svg|frameless|28x28px]] [[File:Zeichen_361-51.svg|frameless|28x28px]] [[Lusk, Dublin|Lusk]] service station\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 4 [[R132 road (Ireland)|R132]] [[Swords, Dublin|Swords]], [[Malahide]], [[Donabate]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 3 [[R125 road (Ireland)|R125]] [[Swords, Dublin|Swords]], [[Ashbourne, County Meath|Ashbourne]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 2 [[Dublin Airport]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 1 [[Malahide]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnkreuz.svg|frameless|30x30px]] [[M50 motorway (Ireland)|M50]] towards Soutbound\n|-\n|[[File:M50_motorway_IE.png|frameless|56x56px]] [[M50 motorway (Ireland)|M50 motorway]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Dublin|Dublin city]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 4 [[R108 road (Ireland)|R108]] [[Ballymun]], [[Naul, Dublin|Naul]]\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 5 [[N2 road (Ireland)|N2]], [[M2 motorway (Ireland)|M2]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Finglas]], [[Ashbourne, County Meath|Ashbourne]], {{Flag|UK}} ([[Derry]])\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 6 [[N3 road (Ireland)|N3]], [[M3 motorway (Ireland)|M3]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Cavan]], [[Navan]], [[Castleknock]], [[Connolly Hospital]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 7 [[N4 road (Ireland)|N4]], [[M4 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M4]], [[M6 motorway (Ireland)|M6]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Galway]], [[Sligo]], [[Westport, County Mayo|Westport]], [[Mullingar]], [[Lucan, Dublin|Lucan]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 9 [[N7 road (Ireland)|N7]], [[M7 motorway (Ireland)|M7]], [[M8 motorway (Ireland)|M8]], [[M9 motorway (Ireland)|M9]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Cork (city)|Cork]], [[Limerick]], [[Waterford]], [[Inchicore]], [[Clondalkin]], [[Naas]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 10 [[R838 road (Ireland)|R838]] [[Ballymount]], Cookstown, Belgard Road\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 11 [[N81 road (Ireland)|N81]] [[Blessington]], [[Templeogue]], [[Tallaght]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 12 [[R113 road (Ireland)|R113]], [[Knocklyon]], Firehouse\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 13 [[R826 road (Ireland)|R826]] [[Sandyford]], [[Dundrum, Dublin|Dundrum]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 14 [[N31 road (Ireland)|N31]] [[D\u00fan Laoghaire]], [[Stillorgan]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 15 [[Cornelscourt]], [[Kilternan]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 16 [[R118 road (Ireland)|R118]], [[Cherrywood, Dublin|Cherrywood]], [[Loughlinstown]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnkreuz.svg|frameless|30x30px]] 17 [[M11 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M11]] towards [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[D\u00fan Laoghaire]]\n|-\n|[[File:M11_motorway_IE.png|frameless|56x56px]] [[M11 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M11 motor