bourne]], {{Flag|UK}} ([[Derry]])\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 6 [[N3 road (Ireland)|N3]], [[M3 motorway (Ireland)|M3]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Cavan]], [[Navan]], [[Castleknock]], [[Connolly Hospital]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 7 [[N4 road (Ireland)|N4]], [[M4 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M4]], [[M6 motorway (Ireland)|M6]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Galway]], [[Sligo]], [[Westport, County Mayo|Westport]], [[Mullingar]], [[Lucan, Dublin|Lucan]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 9 [[N7 road (Ireland)|N7]], [[M7 motorway (Ireland)|M7]], [[M8 motorway (Ireland)|M8]], [[M9 motorway (Ireland)|M9]] [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[Cork (city)|Cork]], [[Limerick]], [[Waterford]], [[Inchicore]], [[Clondalkin]], [[Naas]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 10 [[R838 road (Ireland)|R838]] [[Ballymount]], Cookstown, Belgard Road\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 11 [[N81 road (Ireland)|N81]] [[Blessington]], [[Templeogue]], [[Tallaght]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 12 [[R113 road (Ireland)|R113]], [[Knocklyon]], Firehouse\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 13 [[R826 road (Ireland)|R826]] [[Sandyford]], [[Dundrum, Dublin|Dundrum]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 14 [[N31 road (Ireland)|N31]] [[D\u00fan Laoghaire]], [[Stillorgan]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 15 [[Cornelscourt]], [[Kilternan]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 16 [[R118 road (Ireland)|R118]], [[Cherrywood, Dublin|Cherrywood]], [[Loughlinstown]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnkreuz.svg|frameless|30x30px]] 17 [[M11 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M11]] towards [[Dublin|Dublin center]], [[D\u00fan Laoghaire]]\n|-\n|[[File:M11_motorway_IE.png|frameless|56x56px]] [[M11 motorway (Republic of Ireland)|M11 motorway]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnaus