ss|27x27px]] 16 [[R772 road (Ireland)|R772]] [[Wicklow]] (North), [[Ashford, County Wicklow|Ashford]] (South), [[Rathnew]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 17 [[R772 road (Ireland)|R772]] [[Wicklow]] (Center), [[Rathnew]], [[Rathdrum, County Wicklow|Rathdrum]], [[Glenealy, County Wicklow|Glenealy]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 18 R751 [[Wicklow]] (South), [[Rathdrum, County Wicklow|Rathdrum]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 19 Brittas Bay, [[Redcross]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 20 [[R772 road (Ireland)|R772]] [[Arklow]] (North), [[Redcross]], [[Avoca, County Wicklow|Avoca]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 21 [[R772 road (Ireland)|R772]] [[Arklow]] (South), [[Inch, County Wexford|Inch]], [[Aughrim, County Wicklow|Aughrim]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[County Wexford|Wexford]]\n|[[Arklow]]-[[Enniscorthy]]\n|[[File:Zeichen 376 - Autobahngasthaus (600x600), StVO 1992.svg|frameless|28x28px]] [[File:Zeichen_361-51.svg|frameless|28x28px]] [[Gorey]] service station\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 22 [[R772 road (Ireland)|R772]] [[Gorey]] (North), [[Inch, County Wexford|Inch]], [[Killinierin]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 23 R732 [[R742 road (Ireland)|(R742]], [[R741 road (Ireland)|R741]]) [[Gorey]] (South), [[Courtown]], [[Ballycanew]]\n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 24 [[R772 road (Ireland)|R772]] [[Clogh, County Wexford|Clough]], [[Camolin, County Wexford|Camolin]], [[Ferns, County Wexford|Ferns]] \n\n[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnausfahrt.svg|frameless|27x27px]] 25 [[N30 road (Ireland)|N30]], R744 [[Enniscorthy]], [[Ferns, County Wexford|Ferns]], [[Blackwater, County Wexford|Blackwater]], [[New Ross]], [[Carlow]]\n|-\n|[[File:IRL N11.svg|frameless|50x50px]] [[N11 road (Ireland)|N11 road]]\n|[[Enniscorthy]]-[[Wexford]]\n|[[File:Sinnbild_Autobahnkreuz.svg