026123.pdf 2020-04-01]\n|458\n|199\n|132\n|4\n|14\n|2\n|3\n| \u2014\n|808\n|8251\n|726\n|230\n|27\n|187\n|0\n|43\n|\n|-\n|[https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/31_DGS_boletim_20200402.pdf 2020-04-02]\n|428\n|209\n|116\n|5\n|18\n|0\n|5\n|\u2014\n|783\n|9034\n|1042\n|240\n|22\n|209\n|25\n|68\n|\n|-\n|[https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/32_DGS_boletim_20200403.pdf 2020-04-03]\n|561\n|140\n|125\n|3\n|15\n|2\n|6\n|\u2014\n|852\n|9886\n|1058\n|245\n|37\n|246\n|0\n|68\n|\n|-\n|[https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/33_DGS_boletim_20200404.pdf 2020-04-04]\n|381\n|166\n|86\n|1\n|3\n|1\n|0\n|\u2014\n|638\n|10524\n|1075\n|251\n|20\n|266\n|7\n|75\n|\n|-\n|[https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/34_DGS_boletim_20200405.pdf 2020-04-05]\n|250\n|391\n|70\n|19\n|19\n|1\n|4\n|\u2014\n|754\n|11278\n|1084\n|267\n|29\n|295\n|0\n|75\n|\n|-\n|[https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/34_DGS_boletim_20200406.pdf 2020-04-06]\n|176\n|166\n|79\n|2\n|28\n|0\n|1\n|\u2014\n|452\n|11730\n|1099\n|270\n|16\n|311\n|65\n|140\n|\n|-\n! Total\n!6706\n!3070\n!1521\n!84\n!229\n!52\n!68\n!0\n! \u2014\n!11730\n!1099\n!270\n! \u2014\n!311\n! \u2014\n!140\n!\n|}\n\n== Summary ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+COVID-19\n! colspan=\"2\" |Cases [https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/34_DGS_boletim_20200405.pdf 06-04-2020]\n|-\n!total confirmed cases\n|11730\n|-\n!total not confirmed cases \n|75564\n|-\n!total suspected cases (since January 1, 2020)\n|91794\n|-\n!under surveillance\n|23470\n|-\n!waiting for results\n|4500\n|-\n!recovered\n|140\n|-\n!deaths\n|311\n|-\n|}\n\n{| {{Table}}\n!   !! high fever !! dry cough !! difficult breathing !! headache !! muscular pain !! tiredness\n|-\n! % of cases with symptoms\n| 46%\n| 60%\n| 17%\n| 28%\n| 32%\n| 24%\n|-\n|}\nThere was only reported information regarding the occurrence of symptoms on 77% of confirmed cases.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp