a Landi (June 25/26, 1824 in Florence &ndash; January 5, 1894 in Florence), by whom he had a son:  \n* '''[[Camillo Ruspoli, 4th Marquis of Boadilla del Monte]]'''\n\n== Additional information ==\n=== See also ===\n* [[Ruspoli]]\n\n=== Sources ===\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book |last= Affonso |first= Domingos de Ara\u00fajo|author2=Valdez, Rui Dique Travassos  |title=Livro de Oiro da Nobreza |format=3 volumes |volume=II |year=1938 |location=Lisbon |language=Portuguese }}\n* {{Cite web |url=http://grandesp.org.uk/historia/titulos/titintro.htm |title=Grandes de Espa\u00f1a |accessdate=15 October 2008 |last=Hobbs |first=Nicolas |authorlink= |year=2007 |website= |location= |pages= |language=Spanish |doi= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |quote= }}\n* {{cite book |last=Instituto de Salazar y Castro |others=periodic publication |title=Elenco de Grandezas y Titulos Nobiliarios Espa\u00f1oles |language=Spanish }}\n* {{Cite web |url=http://genealogy.euweb.cz/other/ruspoli.html |title=Ruspoli de Godoy Genealogy |accessdate=15 February 2009 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |year=2007 |website= |location= |pages= |language= |doi= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |quote= }}{{Self-published source|date=August 2012}}{{Better source|date=August 2012}}\n* {{Cite web |url=http://www.geneall.net/H/per_page.php?id=57093 |title=Geneall |accessdate=15 February 2009 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |year=2007 |format= |website= |location= |pages= |language= |doi= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |quote= }}\n{{refend}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-reg|es}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Carlota de Godoy, 2nd Duchess of Sueca|Carlota de Godoy]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title= [[Marquis|Marqu\u00e9s]] of [[Boadilla del Monte]] |years=1886-1893}}\n{{s-aft|after={{nowrap|[[Camillo Ruspoli, 4th Marquis of Boadilla del Monte|Camillo Ruspoli]]}}}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ruspoli, Luigi 03}}\n[[Category:1828 births]]\n[[Category:1893 deaths]]\n[[Category:House of Ruspoli|Luigi]]\n[[Category:Marquesses of Boadilla del Monte|Luigi 03]]\n\n\n{