31 |title=Potvr\u0111eno jo\u0161 devet pozitivnih na koronavirus u Hercegovini i srednjoj Bosni |website=Klix.ba |language=bs-BA |access-date=3 April 2020}}</ref> [[Gornji Vakuf-Uskoplje]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bugojno-danas.info/prvi-slucaj-zaraze-korona-virusom-u-gornjem-vakufu-uskoplju/ |title=Prvi slu\u010daj zaraze Korona virusom u Gornjem Vakufu-Uskoplju |website=Bugojno-danas.info |language=bs-BA |access-date=30 March 2020}}</ref> [[Novi Travnik]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/soliter-u-novom-travniku-pod-blokadom-zbog-zarazenog-muskarca-obustavljen-rad-bnt-a/200322053 |title=Soliter u Novom Travniku pod blokadom zbog zara\u017eenog mu\u0161karca, obustavljen rad BNT-a |website=Klix.ba |language=bs-BA |access-date=22 March 2020}}</ref> [[Vitez]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vitez.info/potvrdena-prva-zarazena-osoba-iz-viteza/ |title=Potvr\u0111ena prva zara\u017eena osoba iz Viteza |date=1 April 2020 |website=Vitez.info |language=hr |access-date=1 April 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 23\n| align=\"right\"| 1\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Herzegovina-Neretva Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[\u010capljina]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dnevnik.ba/vijesti/prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-u-capljini |title=Prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa u \u010capljini |date=4 April 2020 |website=Dnevnik.ba |language=hr |access-date=5 April 2020}}</ref> [[\u010citluk]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/nova-cetiri-slucaja-koronavirusa-u-hercegovini-jedna-osoba-je-iz-citluka/200326203 |title=Nova \u010detiri slu\u010daja koronavirusa u Hercegovini, jedna osoba je iz \u010citluka |website=Klix.ba |language=bs-BA |access-date=26 March 2020}}</ref> [[Jablanica, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Jablanica]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/potvrdjen-prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-u-jablanici-te-novi-u-mostaru-i-citluku/200401052 |title=Potvr\u0111en prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa u Jablanici te novi u Mostaru i \u010citluku |website=Klix.ba |language=bs-BA |access-date=1 April 2020}}</ref> [[Konjic]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-u-bh-nogometu/355538 |title=Prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa u bh. nogometu |website=SportSport.ba |language=bs-BA}}</ref> [[Mostar]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bhrt.ba/prvi-slucaj-zaraze-koronavirusom-u-mostaru/1115172/ |title=Prvi slu\u010daj zaraze koronavirusom u Mostaru |date=17 March 2020 |website=BHRT |language=bs-BA}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 128\n| align=\"right\"| 6\n| align=\"right\"| 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Posavina Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Domaljevac-\u0160amac]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fena.ba/article/1140956/the-fourth-case-of-coronavirus-infection-confirmed-in-fbih-today |title=The fourth case of coronavirus infection confirmed in FBiH today |website=FENA |access-date=17 March 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 3\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n| align=\"right\"| 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Sarajevo Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Centar, Sarajevo|Centar]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\" /> [[Had\u017ei\u0107i]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\" /> [[Ilid\u017ea]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\" /> [[Ilija\u0161]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\" /> [[Novi Grad, Sarajevo|Novi Grad]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\">{{Cite web |url=https://zis-ks.maps.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/8cde5734d1f04b8aa32f5840c70b7b82 |title=Operations Dashboard for ArcGIS |website=zis-ks.maps.arcgis.com}}</ref> [[Novo Sarajevo]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\" /> [[Stari Grad, Sarajevo|Stari Grad]],<ref name=\"zis-ks\" /> [[Vogo\u0161\u0107a]]<ref name=\"zis-ks\" />\n| align=\"right\"| 53\n| align=\"right\"| 4\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Tuzla Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Banovi\u0107i]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://rtvtk.ba/prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-u-banovicima/ |title=Prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa u Banovi\u0107ima {{!}} RTVTK |last=Dautovi