a]]\n| align=\"right\" | 3\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" |[[Kne\u017eevo, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Kne\u017eevo]]\n| align=\"right\" | 6\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Kotor Varo\u0161]]\n| align=\"right\"| 7\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Kozarska Dubica]]\n| align=\"right\"| 8\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Lakta\u0161i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 26\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 6\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"|[[Mili\u0107i, Republika Srpska|Mili\u0107i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Modri\u010da]]\n| align=\"right\" | 3\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Mrkonji\u0107 Grad]]\n| align=\"right\" | 4\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Novi Grad, Republika Srpska|Novi Grad]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Pale, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Pale]]\n| align=\"right\" | 2\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Prijedor]]\n| align=\"right\"| 3\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Prnjavor, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Prnjavor]]\n| align=\"right\" | 6\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Ribnik, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Ribnik]]\n| align=\"right\"| 5\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Srbac]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[\u0160ekovi\u0107i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[\u0160ipovo]]\n| align=\"right\" | 11\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Tesli\u0107]]\n| align=\"right\" | 9\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Zvornik]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" align=\"right\"| Total\n! align=\"right\"| 346\n! align=\"right\"| 11\n! align=\"right\"| 56\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\"|{{small|''As of 7 April 2020}}<ref name=\"JZU Institut za javno zdravstvo RS\" /><ref name=\"koronausrpskoj\" />\n|}\n\nAs of 7 April 2020, people from following [[Cantons of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina|cantons]] and municipalities in the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina have been infected:\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Canton\n! scope=\"col\" | Municipalities affected\n! scope=\"col\" | Cases\n! scope=\"col\" | Deaths\n! scope=\"col\" | Recoveries<ref name=\"covid-19.ba\" />\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Canton 10]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Livno]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.livno-online.com/zupanija/34890-prvi-slucaj-korona-virusa-u-livnu |title=Prvi slu\u010daj korona virusa u Livnu |last=User |first=Super |website=Livno Online |language=hr-hr |access-date=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 10\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Bosnian-Podrinje Canton Gora\u017ede|Bosnian-Podrinje Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Gora\u017ede]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://faktor.ba/vijest/prvi-slucaj-u-gorazdu-svi-koji-su-bili-u-kontaktu-sa-direktoricom-ginexa-moraju-se-javiti-na-broj-121-/74984 |title=Prvi slu\u010daj u Gora\u017edu: